These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-1::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: woodworking, video-games, board-games
1. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is not to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##8
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is video-games##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |       1       |    2    |    3     |
| Hobby   | board-games | video-games | woodworking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-2::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, ambient, soul
1. the fan of soul is not to the left of the fan of house##8
2. the fan of soul is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3     |
| Music-Genre   | house | soul | ambient |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-8-3::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: daisy, balloon-flower, lily
1. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1
2. the person who growsdaisy is not to the right of the person who growslily##8

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |   2   |  3  |
| Flower   | balloon-flower | daisy | lily |

